         MACRO           DEFINE FSRTN TERMINAL ATTRIBUTES SUPPLY.
&NAME   @FST   &DUMMY
.*
.* @FST MACRO : DEFINE FSRTN TERMINAL ATTRIBUTES SUPPLY (SEE FSRTN).
.* ------------
.*
.* AUTHOR :    P.A. MOINIL
.* --------    COMPUTING CENTRE
.*             J.R.C. - ISPRA ESTABLISHMENT
.*             21020 ISPRA (VA), ITALY
.*
&NAME    DC    XL8'0'
FSPRMSZE EQU   &NAME+0,2           PRIMARY (DEFAULT) SCREEN SIZE
FSPRMROW EQU   &NAME+0,1                ROWS
FSPRMCOL EQU   &NAME+1,1                COLUMNS
FSALTSZE EQU   &NAME+2,2           ALTERNATE SCREEN SIZE
FSALTROW EQU   &NAME+2,1                ROWS
FSALTCOL EQU   &NAME+3,1                COLUMNS
FSATTRIB EQU   &NAME+4,4           TERMINAL ATTRIBUTES
FSATTRB0 EQU   &NAME+4,1                BYTE 0 - RESERVED
FSATTRB1 EQU   &NAME+5,1                BYTE 1 - RESERVED
FSATTRB2 EQU   &NAME+6,1                BYTE 2 - RESERVED
FSATTRB3 EQU   &NAME+7,1                BYTE 3
FSTASCII EQU   X'02'               DEVICE SUPPORTS : 1=ASCII, 0=EBCDIC
FSTQUERY EQU   X'01'               READ PARTITION (QUERY) IS SUPPORTED
         MEND
